y.%20That's%20despite%201%2C000%20companies%20announcing%20they%20were%20voluntarily%20cutting%20back%20on%20operations%20merely%20two%20months%20after%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20started.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20for%20lack%20of%20trying%3A%20More%20than%202%2C000%20companies%20were%20seeking%20approval%20to%20exit%20the%20Russian%20market%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F77368014-1397-4a08-901d-1f996e66d627%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20March%2C%20but%20the%20progress%20has%20been%20slow%20due%20to%20logistical%20delays.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20well-known%20of%20these%20corporate%20exits%20was%20from%20McDonald's%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-quits-russia-30-years-ukraine-war-putin-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esold%20off%20its%20operations%20in%20Russia%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20in%20the%20country.%20McDonald's%20replacement%20is%20a%20copycat%20chain%20that%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-russia-replacement-vkusno-tochka-fast-food-customer-reviews-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereplaced%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Mac%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Hit.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20who%20have%20varying%20degrees%20of%20active%20operations%20in%20Russia%20cannot%20simply%20pack%20up%20and%20go%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20business%20and%20non-business-related%20reasons%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-exit-foreign-company-difficulties-ukraine-war-explainer-2023-3%5C%22%3Eoperational%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20policy%20challenges%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Insider%20reported%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Potanin%C2%A0did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-businessmen-acquire-western-companies-exit-exodus-asset-bargain-prices-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689675220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b6369c76558a00189d0f4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-businessmen-acquire-western-companies-exit-exodus-asset-bargain-prices-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20regulations%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20foreign%20firms%20to%20leave%20Russia%2C%20and%20force%20firms%20trying%20to%20leave%20to%20sell%20their%20operations%20at%20a%20large%20discount.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kteo%40insider.com%20(Kai%20Xiang%20Teo%2CHuileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-businessmen-acquire-western-companies-exit-exodus-asset-bargain-prices-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Portal%20Launched%20To%20Help%2010%20Crore%20Sahara%20Depositors%20Get%20Refund%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20was%20launched%20today%2C%20bringing%20much-awaited%20relief%20to%20as%20many%20as%2010%20crore%20people.%20The%20portal%20will%20facilitate%20the%20process%20of%20refunding%20the%20money%20that%20depositors%20put%20in%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20of%20returning%20the%20money%20of%20depositors%2C%20which%20was%20stuck%20in%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group%2C%20has%20started%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20while%20launching%20the%20refund%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20said%20that%20initially%20Rs%2010%2C000%20will%20be%20returned%20to%20investors%20on%20a%20trial%20basis.%20Gradually%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20refund%20may%20be%20increased%20if%20the%20trial%20succeeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%201.7%20crore%20investors%20can%20register%20on%20the%20refund%20portal%20and%20claim%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20in%20the%20first%20phase.%20According%20to%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20there%20are%204%20crore%20depositors%20who%20are%20eligible%20to%20get%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20assured%20Sahara%20depositors%20that%20their%20money%20is%20safe%20and%20that%20they%20will%20receive%20a%20refund%20within%2045%20days%20of%20registering%20on%20the%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20portal%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20will%20work%20by%20linking%20your%20Aadhaar%20number%20to%20your%20mobile%20phone%20number%20and%20bank%20account.%20You%20will%20also%20need%20to%20provide%20receipt%20details.%20Once%20you%20have%20done%20this%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20download%20a%20form%2C%20fill%20it%20out%2C%20and%20re-upload%20it%20to%20the%20portal.%20The%20refund%20process%20will%20then%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20will%20it%20take%20to%20get%20a%20refund%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20money%20will%20be%20deposited%20into%20the%20bank%20account%20of%20the%20claimant%20within%2045%20days.%20The%20Home%20Minister%20urged%20to%20use%20the%20Common%20Services%20Centers%20(CSC)%20digital%20services%20in%20case%20of%20any%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20will%20CRCS%20Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20is%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20members%20of%20the%20cooperatives.%20The%20portal%20will%20help%20address%20the%20genuine%20claims%20of%20depositors%20who%20had%20invested%20money%20in%20Sahara%20Group's%20cooperative%20societies%20namely%20-%20Sahara%20Credit%20Cooperative%20Society%20Ltd%2C%20Saharayan%20Universal%20Multipurpose%20Society%20Ltd%2C%20Humara%20India%20Credit%20Cooperative%20Society%20Ltd%20and%20Stars%20Multipurpose%20Cooperative%20Society%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20dated%2029th%20March%202023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20be%20transferred%20out%20of%20the%20'Sahara-SEBI%20Refund%20Account'%20to%20the%20Central%20Registrar%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies%20(CRCS)%20for%20disbursement%20against%20the%20legitimate%20dues%20of%20the%20genuine%20depositors%20of%20Sahara%20Group%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689675060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fijsje7l_sahara-chief-subrata-roy-650_625x300_31_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20was%20launched%20today%2C%20bringing%20much-awaited%20relief%20to%20as%20many%20as%2010%20crore%20people.%20The%20portal%20will%20facilitate%20the%20process%20of%20refunding%20the%20money%20that%20depositors%20put%20in%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I-N-D-I-A'%