ted%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20from%202004%20to%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20two%20subcommittees%20will%20be%20formed%3A%20one%20to%20finalise%20the%20common%20minimum%20program%20and%20communication%20points%2C%20and%20the%20other%20to%20plan%20joint%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-26-opposition-parties-that-have-formed-mega-alliance-for-2024-lok-sabha-election-4217778%5C%22%3Eopposition%3C%2Fa%3E%20events%2C%20rallies%2C%20and%20conventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20besides%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20opposition%20meet%20is%20being%20attended%20by%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Chief%20Ministers%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20and%20RJD%20Chief%20Lalu%20Prasad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Janata%20Dal-Secular%20(JDS)%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20opposition%20meeting.%20Although%20Mr%20Pawar%20arrived%20in%20Bengaluru%20today%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20will%20attend%20the%20meeting%20or%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20parties%20having%20the%20will%20and%20guts%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20are%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike-minded%20opposition%20parties%20shall%20closely%20work%20together%20to%20foster%20an%20agenda%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20inclusive%20development%20and%20national%20welfare.%20We%20want%20to%20free%20the%20people%20of%20India%20from%20the%20autocratic%20and%20anti-people%20politics%20of%20hate%2C%20division%2C%20economic%20inequality%20and%20loot...%20United%20We%20Stand%2C%20for%20this%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%20coincides%20with%20the%20NDA%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%2C%20w