ssault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20a%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%2C%20354A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20354D%20(stalking)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tomar%20was%20charged%20with%20offences%20under%20IPC%20sections%20109%20(abetment%20of%20any%20offence%2C%20if%20the%20act%20abetted%20is%20committed%20in%20consequence%2C%20and%20where%20no%20express%20provision%20is%20made%20for%20its%20punishment)%2C%20354%2C%20354A%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20counsel%20alleged%20media%20trail%2C%20to%20which%20the%20judge%20said%20he%20may%20move%20an%20application%20before%20the%20high%20court%20or%20trial%20court.%20The%20court%20will%20pass%20an%20appropriate%20order%20on%20the%20application%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20move%20any%20application%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20present%20case%2C%20another%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%20Mr%20Singh%20pursuant%20to%20allegations%20made%20by%20a%20minor%20wrestler%2C%20which%20was%20registered%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%20She%20was%20among%20the%20seven%20female%20grapplers%20who%20had%20accused%20Mr%20Singh%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20FIRs%20mentioned%20several%20alleged%20instances%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20like%20inappropriate%20touching%2C%20groping%2C%20stalking%20and%20intimidation%20by%20Mr%20Singh%20at%20different%20times%20and%20places%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689674640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fco8cg3tk_brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-650_625x300_31_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrestling-federation-of-india-chief-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-gets-interim-ba