icy%20to%20eliminate%20student%20debt%20when%20borrowers%20are%20in%20long-term%20default%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECreate%20a%20policy%20to%20eliminate%20student%20debt%20when%20the%20department%20does%20not%20have%20updated%20contact%20information%20for%20borrowers%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStop%20requiring%20a%20borrower%20repay%20the%20full%20amount%20of%20debt%20when%20they%20enter%20default%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BExhaust%20all%20other%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20determining%20if%20a%20borrower%20is%20eligible%20for%20relief%2C%20before%20sending%20their%20debt%20to%20collections%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAllow%20borrowers%20who%20are%20approved%20for%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20while%20in%20default%20to%20be%20automatically%20pulled%20out%20of%20default%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStrengthen%20contract%20terms%20with%20debt%20collectors%20to%20prevent%20predatory%20practices%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Warren%20wrote%20in%20her%20letter%2C%20when%20a%20borrower%20enters%20default%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20requires%20them%20to%20repay%20their%20full%20outstanding%20student-loan%20balance%20%E2%80%94%20including%20principal%2C%20interest%2C%20and%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRequiring%20borrowers%20to%20repay%20the%20full%20amount%20of%20debt%20upon%20default%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20past-due%20balance%20on%20an%20IDR%20plan%2C%20significantly%20increases%20both%20the%20total%20repayment%20amount%20and%20the%20time%20required%20to%20settle%20the%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20Warren%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20those%20in%20default%2C%20the%20department%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-i-qualify-for-fresh-start-student-loan-debt-forgiveness-2022-8%5C%22%3Eannounced%20a%20%26quot%3BFresh%20Start%26quot%3B%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20restore%207.5%20million%20borrowers%20behind%20on%20payments%20to%20good%20standing%20once%20payments%20resume.%20The%20benefits%20of%20the%20plan%20will%20last%20one%