dren%20to%20be%20with%20her%20lover%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20flee%20to%20Delhi%20when%20she%20was%20arrested%2C%20Noida%20police%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20came%20to%20India%20through%20Nepal%20with%20her%20four%20children%20to%20live%20with%20Sachin%20Meena%2C%20who%20she%20had%20met%20in%202019%20while%20playing%20the%20online%20game%20PlayerUnknown's%20Battlegrounds%20(PUBG).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20was%20arrested%20for%20illegally%20entering%20India%20without%20a%20visa%20and%20was%20interrogated%20by%20the%20Anti-Terror%20Squad%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20FIR%20filed%20by%20Noida%20police%2C%20Seema%20told%20them%20that%20she%20couldn't%20get%20a%20visa%20to%20India%20so%20she%20travelled%20to%20Nepal%20from%20where%20she%20took%20a%20bus%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20reached%20the%20Yamuna%20Expressway%20with%20my%20four%20children%20on%20May%2013%20from%20where%20Sachin%20took%20us%20to%20a%20rented%20house%20in%20Greater%20Noida's%20Mohalla%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20for%20sheltering%20the%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20told%20police%20that%20he%20introduced%20Seema%20to%20his%20father%20and%20told%20him%20of%20his%20intention%20to%20marry%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSachin's%20father%20said%20that%20he%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20marry%20me%20only%20if%20adapted%20to%20the%20Indian%20way%20of%20living.%20I%20agreed%20to%20his%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%20Sachin%20went%20back%20to%20his%20hometown%20and%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20his%20father%20Netrapal%20came%20to%20her%20house%2C%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20took%20me%20to%20a%20court%20in%20Bulandshahr%20to%20meet%20a%20lawyer%20to%20start%20the%20court%20marriage%20process.%20When%20I%20showed%20them%20my%20papers%2C%20the%20lawyer%20told%20me%20that%20I%20could%20not%20marry%20Sachi