with%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20asking%20for%20internet%20to%20be%20restored%2C%20against%20which%20the%20government%20had%20moved%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20violence%20first%20began%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20an%20order%20by%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%2C%20asking%20the%20state%20government%20to%20look%20into%20the%20process%20of%20giving%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status.%20In%20the%20days%20that%20followed%2C%20widespread%20destruction%20has%20led%20to%20almost%20140%20deaths%20and%20close%20to%2060%2C000%20people%20were%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Ftwin-bandhs-called-by-two-different-outfits-hit-life-in-several-districts-of-manipur%2Fcid%2F1952728%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20influential%20UNC%20%E2%80%93%20the%20apex%20body%20of%2020%20Naga%20tribes%20residing%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20had%20called%20a%2012-hour%20bandh%20from%206%20am%20across%20Naga%20areas%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20murder%20of%20a%2055-year-old%20Naga%20woman%20in%20Imphal%20East%20on%20July%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftwo-killed-in-separate-incidents-as-violence-continues-in-manipur%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20July%2016%2C%20in%20Imphal%20East%2C%20the%20woman%2C%20Lucy%20Maring%2C%20who%20had%20a%20mental%20illness%20was%20found%20dead.%20She%20had%20been%20shot%20and%20her%20face%20disfigured.%20Nine%20people%20including%20five%20women%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%2C%20according%20to%20Manipur%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UNC%20has%20blamed%20the%20Meitei%20group%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20the%20women%20activists%20for%