on's%20mantra%20is%20-%20of%20the%20family%2C%20by%20the%20family%2C%20for%20the%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20comes%20as%2026%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20gathered%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20devise%20a%20strategy%20to%20take%20on%20BJP%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20dubbed%20the%20ongoing%20Opposition%20conclave%20a%20meeting%20of%20%26quot%3Bhardcore%20corrupts%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20saying%20that%20this%20gathering%20is%20to%20promote%20corruption.%20The%20opposition%20parties%20have%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20DMK%20despite%20corruption%20cases%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20also%20mum%20on%20panchayat%20poll%20violence%20in%20West%20Bengal%20despite%20attacks%20on%20their%20cadre%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(opposition%20parties)%20are%20not%20concerned%20about%20the%20development%20of%20the%20children%20of%20the%20country's%20poor.%20Their%20common%20minimum%20programme%20is%20to%20increase%20corruption%20for%20their%20family.%20Democracy%20means%20'of%20the%20people%2C%20by%20the%20people%2C%20for%20the%20people'.%20But%20these%20dynastic%20parties%20have%20the%20mantra%20of%20'of%20the%20family%2C%20by%20the%20family%2C%20for%20the%20family'.%20For%20them%2C%20their%20family%20is%20first%2C%20and%20the%20nation%20is%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20building%20that%20PM%20inaugurated%20in%20Port%20Blair%2C%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20around%20Rs%20710%20crore%2C%20will%20boost%20connectivity%20of%20the%20island.%20With%20a%20total%20built%20up%20area%20of%20around%2040%2C800%20sq%20m%2C%20the%20new%20terminal%20building%20will%20be%20capable%20of%20handling%20about%2050%20lakh%20passengers%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20building%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20shell%2C%20depicting%20the%20natural%20environs%20of%20the%20