0his%20501-minute%20innings.%C2%A0His%20impressive%20knock%20of%20171%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20victory%20against%20West%20Indies%20in%20the%20two-match%20Test%20series%20at%20Windsor%20Park.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathour%20was%20impressed%20with%20Jaiswal's%20performance%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20after%20he%20followed%20up%20on%20his%20successful%20IPL%202023%20season%20with%20Rajasthan%20Royals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20a%20selector%20before%2C%20so%20whenever%20you%20pick%20a%20player%20you%20should%20pick%20him%20with%20the%20intent%20that%20he%20will%20play%20for%20India%20for%20the%20next%2010%20years.%20He%20definitely%20has%20the%20potential.%20For%20me%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20(even%20though)%20I%20haven't%20worked%20with%20Yashasvi%20before%2C%20was%20that%20I%20had%20seen%20him%20scoring%20runs%20at%20the%20IPL%2C%20you%20saw%20how%20dynamic%20a%20batsman%20he%20is%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20stroke%20player%20he%20is.%20But%20he%20managed%20to%20change%20the%20game%20according%20to%20the%20situation%20of%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathour%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20ahead%20of%20the%20second%20Test.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20took%20his%20time%20on%20the%20crease%20before%20he%20went%20on%20to%20open%20his%20account%20and%20then%20shifted%20gears%20to%20reach%20the%20three-figure%20mark%20on%20his%20Test%20debut.%20However%2C%20one%20thing%20that%20came%20to%20notice%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20play%20against%20his%20natural%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20the%20hosts%2C%20Jaiswal%20didn't%20go%20to%20play%20his%20usual%20self%20before%20lunch.%20He%20took%20time%20and%20scored%20a%20few%20runs%20after%20facing%20almost%2090%20deliveries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathour%20lauded%20Jaiswal%20for%20his%20change%20in%20approach%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20second%20day%2C%20he%20scored%20some%2020%20runs%20off%2090%