A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-silent-on-bengal-panchayat-polls-violence-pms-top-quotes-4217482%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sensex%20Up%20Over%203%2C600%20Points%20In%20A%20Month%3A%20Whats%20Driving%20The%20Rally%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20stock%20markets%20are%20on%20a%20roll%2C%20with%20the%20benchmark%20BSE%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty%20hitting%20fresh%20highs%20yet%20again%20on%20Tuesday%20amid%20sustained%20investor%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20month%2C%20the%20Sensex%20has%20gained%20over%203%2C600%20points%2C%20or%205.7%20per%20cent%2C%20to%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%2066%2C985.50%20on%20Tuesday.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Nifty%20has%20jumped%20more%20than%201%2C000%20points%2C%20or%205.1%20per%20cent%2C%20during%20the%20same%20period%20to%20hit%20its%20peak%20of%2019%2C811.25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20attribute%20the%20sharp%20spike%20in%20indices%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%20like%20strong%20foreign%20inflows%2C%20support%20from%20global%20markets%2C%20easing%20US%20inflation%20hinting%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20rate-hike%20cycle%20and%20expectations%20of%20a%20solid%20earnings%20season%20back%20at%20home%20for%20the%20quarter-ended%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20factors%20induce%20optimism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20markets%2C%20especially%20Asian%20equity%20indices%2C%20are%20on%20the%20rise%20after%20the%20US%20inflation%20slid%20to%20a%20two-year%20low%20in%20June.%20The%20US%20consumer%20price%20index%20(CPI)%20rose%203%20per%20cent%20in%20June%20compared%20with%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20while%20the%20core%20measure%20advanced%20just%204.8%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20lowest%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20analysts%20expect%20that%20the%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20will%20still%20go%20ahead%20with%20one%20more%20rate%20hike%20in%20its%20July%2026%20meeting%2C%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20further%20increase%20in%20the%20September%20meeting%20appears%20to%20be%20receding%20with%20cooling%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20that%2C%20global%20markets%20are%20also%20being%20supported%20by%20improving%20economic%20outlook%20after%20the%20US%20reported%20better-than-expected%20quarterly%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20growth%20of%202%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%20and%20declining%20jobless%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraging%20data%20on%20all%20fronts%20%E2%80%93%20growth%2C%20inflation%20and%20jobless%20claims%20--%20have%20helped%20undercut%20expectations%20that%20the%20US%20was%20heading%20towards%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeign%20Investor%20repose%20faith%20in%20Indian%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Indian%20markets%20are%20enjoying%20unwavering%20support%20from%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPIs)%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20in%20sustaining%20the%20positive%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20exchanges%20show%20that%20foreign%20investors%20purchased%20a%20net%20%245.7%20billion%20in%20Indian%20equities%20in%20June%2C%20the%20biggest%20such%20inflow%20since%20August%202022%2C%20on%20expectations%20of%20a%20bumper%20earnings%20season%20and%20normal%20monsoons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFPIs%20have%20also%20remained%20net%20buyers%20in%20Indian%20stock%20markets%20for%20the%20fifth%20straight%20month%20in%20July%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Securities%20Depository%20Ltd%20(NSDL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrong%20growth%20projections%20for%20India%20by%20various%20global%20agencies%20have%20made%20Indian%20stock%20markets%20a%20bright%20spot%20for%20foreign%20investors%20in%20an%20otherwise%20bleak%20global%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrong%20Q1%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobust%20earnings%20growth%20forecast%20for%20the%20quarter%20ending%20June%202023%20(Q1FY24)%20is%20also%20fuelling%20the%20rally%20in%20Indian%20stocks.%20On%20Monday%2C%20India's%20largest%20private%20sector%20lender%20HDFC%20Bank%20Ltd%20reported%2030%20per%20cent%20growth%20in%20net%20profit%20for%20the%20June%20quarter%2C%20beating%20estimates.%20Before%20that%2C%20top%20software%20exporter%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20Ltd%20(TCS)%20also%20posted%20better-than-expected%20growth%20in%20Q1%20net%20profit%20at%2017%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20early%20indicators%20are%20positive%2C%20markets%20seem%20to%20be%20gearing%20up%20for%20a%20strong%20earnings%20season%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20next%20leg%20of%20the%20rally.%20Though%2C%20analysts%20advise%20caution%20as%20any%20negative%20surprise%20on%20the%20economic%20front%20can%20trigger%20a%20strong%20sell-off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689661320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fucl9a4jc_sensex-reuters_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsensex-up-over-3-600-points-in-a-month-what-s-driving-the-rally-4217463%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20stock%20markets%20are%20on%20a%20roll%2C%20with%20the%20benchmark%20BSE%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty%20hitting%20fresh%20highs%20yet%20again%20on%20Tuesday%20amid%20sustained%20investor%20optimism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsensex-up-over-3-600-points-in-a-month-what-s-driving-the-rally-4217463%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsensex-up-over-3-600-points-in-a-month-what-s-driving-the-rally-4217463%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsensex-up-over-3-600-points-in-a-month-what-s-driving-the-rally-4217463%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TNT%20Sports%20Goes%20Live%2C%20Replacing%20BT%20Sport%2C%20With%20Discovery%2B%20as%20U.K.%20Platform%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publish