se%20officials%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20persists%2C%20per%20the%20FT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuurbier's%20contract%20to%20manage%20the%20domain%20was%20set%20to%20expire%20on%20Monday.%20This%20means%20Mali's%20government%20now%20has%20access%20to%20the%20domain%20and%20further%20emails%20received%2C%20per%20the%20FT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20given%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2F2023%2F02%2F28%2Frussia-s-growing-footprint-in-africa-s-sahel-region-pub-89135%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignificant%20support%20to%20the%20Malian%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20weapons%2C%20diplomatic%20backing%2C%20and%20help%20with%20information%20and%20disinformation%20campaigns.%20The%20Wagner%20Group%2C%20the%20Russian%20mercenary%20company%20linked%20to%20the%20Kremlin%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F05%2F31%2Fworld%2Fafrica%2Fmali-massacre-investigation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20operates%20in%20Mali.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Pentagon%20spokesperson%2C%20Lt.%20Cmdr.%20Tim%20Gorman%2C%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20the%20Defense%20Department%20%26quot%3Bis%20aware%20of%20this%20issue%20and%20takes%20all%20unauthorized%20disclosures%20of%20controlled%20national%20security%20information%20or%20controlled%20unclassified%20information%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20military%20email%20accounts%20also%20notify%20personnel%20if%20they%20try%20sending%20a%20message%20to%20addresses%20with%20the%20%26quot%3B.ml%26quot%3B%20domain%2C%20and%20will%20automatically%20block%20the%20email%20from%20being%20sent%2C%20Gorman%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20and%20the%20Malian%20government%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi