07%2F15153652%2FNovember-2022-FIR.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663348%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20FIR%20filed%20in%20November%202022%20in%20the%20gambling%20case.%20Photo%3A%20Huneza%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20not%20mentioned%20in%20that%20FIR.%20Mirota%20said%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20added%20to%20the%20FIR%20after%20he%20died%20to%20cover%20up%20his%20death.%20Notably%2C%20the%20said%20FIR%20was%20filed%20by%20complainant%20Saddam%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20alleged%20custodial%20killing%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20family%E2%80%99s%20plight%3A%20No%20government%20aid%20provided%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReena%20Bano%2C%2030%2C%20is%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20widow.%20She%20is%20devastated%20by%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20innocent.%20He%20was%20on%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20my%20mother%20when%20the%20policemen%20held%20him.%20He%20was%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20of%20the%20family.%20His%20death%20has%20led%20us%20to%20live%20on%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20mercy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20administration%20didn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20us%20with%20any%20aid.%20I%20have%20become%20lonely.%20My%20children%20are%20helpless%20without%20their%20father%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20continued%2C%20breaking%20into%20tears.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20thought%20of%20the%20old%20days%20made%20Bano%20nostalgic.%20She%20said%20they%20were%20a%20happy%20family%20living%20together%20in%20harmony%20without%20any%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20grief%20surrounding%20us.%20We%20are%20helpless%20even%20for%20food.%20My%20children%20cry%20for%20their%20father.%20They%20ask%20questions%2C%20%E2%80%98Do%20we%20deserve%20to%20live%20in%20this%20poor%20condition%3F%E2%80%99%20We%20are%20living%20in%20fear.%20They%20killed%20my%20innocent%20husband.%20They%20might%20kill%20us%20for%20not%20signing%20a%20compromise.%20I%20only%20want%20justice%20for%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fstruggles-widows-men-custodial-death-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3EThe%20Struggles%20of%20Widows%20of%20Men%20Who%20Died%20in%20Custody%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20her%20in-laws%20have%20been%20receiving%20death%20threats%20from%20the%20start.%20She%20demands%20a%20job%20from%20the%20administration%20to%20compensate%20for%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20give%20a%20good%20education%20to%20my%20children%20and%20take%20care%20of%20my%20in-laws.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20independent%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMunawwar%20is%20struggling%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20his%20family.%20Calamities%20are%20no%20stranger%20to%20him%20%E2%80%93%20he%20lost%20his%20elder%20son%20and%20now%20another%20of%20his%20sons%20met%20with%20a%20brutal%20accident%20while%20searching%20for%20livelihood.%20Bedridden%2C%20his%20voice%20cracked%20as%20he%20narrated%20his%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIsrael%20used%20to%20run%20the%20family.%20We%20are%20very%20poor%20now.%20We%20get%20food%20for%20the%20morning%20and%20have%20no%20hopes%20for%20the%20evening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20son%20was%20innocent%20and%20there%20are%20no%20criminal%20records%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20his%20family%20was%20put%20under%20political%20pressure%20to%20take%20their%20complaint%20back.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20prefer%20dying%20to%20compromising%20in%20this%20situation.%20I%20only%20want%20justice%20for%20my%20son%20and%20his%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15154454%2FChildren-and-father-of-Israel-Khan.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15154454%2FChildren-and-father-of-Israel-Khan.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15154454%2FChildren-and-father-of-Israel-Khan-300x165.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663350%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22352%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMunawwar%20Khan%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20four%20children.%20Photo%3A%20Huneza%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGuna%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Rakesh%20Sagar%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20in%20the%20case%20but%20the%20accused%20have%20not%20been%20arrested%20due%20to%20some%20new%20facts%20coming%20to%20light.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20accepted%20in%20the%20inquiry%20report%20that%20the%20man%20died%20in%20police%20custody.%20The%20CSP%20%5Bchief%20superintendent%20of%20police%5D%20was%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20but%20as%20per%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20inquiry%20report%2C%20we%20have%20handed%20over%20the%20diary%20to%20SDPO%20%5BSub-Divisional%20Police%20Officer%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20proper%20investigation%20is%20done%20when%20a%20case%20is%20registered%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20the%20accused%20committed%20the%20crime%20or%20not.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20report%20was%20released%20recently.%20We%20will%20try%20to%20wind%20up%20the%20case%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESDPO%20Vivek%20Asthana%20said%20that%20the%20FIR%20was%20registered%20before%20the%20magisterial%20inquiry%20report%2C%20which%20lies%20with%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20diary%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20me%20recently.%20We%20are%20investigating%20the%20case%20and%20even%20took%20statements%20from%20key%20witnesses%20a%20few%20days%20back.%20The%20witnesses%20haven%E2%80%99t%20informed%20me%20about%20any%20threats.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20such%20thing%2C%20then%20they%20may%20register%20a%20separate%20FIR%20with%20the%20Cantt%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asthana%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CSP%20investigated%20the%20case%20and%20registered%20an%20FIR%2C%20and%20the%20case%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20me%20later.%20We%20will%20try%20to%20resolve%20it%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDelaying%20an%20FIR%20is%20criminal%20neglect%3A%20Ex-bureaucrat%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEx-bureaucrat%20Swaran%20Ram%20Darapuri%20said%20that%20an%20immediate%20FIR%20is%20mandatory%20in%20the%20case%20of%20custodial%20killing%2C%20which%20was%20not%20done%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20case.%20He%20added%20that%20delaying%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20and%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20orders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20criminal%20neglect%20to%20delay%20the%20FIR%20for%20three%20months.%20The%20supervising%20authorities%20should%20also%20be%20held%20liable%20along%20with%20the%20perpetrators%2C%20as%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20jurisdiction%20within%20their%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darapuri%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20threats%20against%20family%20and%20witnesses%20are%20obvious.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20must%20ensure%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20undue%20pressure%20or%20threats%20against%20them.%20Those%20who%20are%20accused%20are%20not%20enough%2C%20because%20nothing%20goes%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20SHO.%20He%20should%20also%20be%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20but%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20protect%20him.%20The%20state%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20compensating%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darapuri%20concluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689658247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-arrests-six-months-after-custodial-death-despite-fir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Six%20months%20after%20Israel%20Khan%20died%20in%20police%20custody%20and%20three%20months%20after%20police%20filed%20an%20FIR%20in%20the%20case%2C%20no%20arrests%20have%20been%20made.%20His%20family%20alleges%20they%20have%20received%20death%20threats%20from%20when%20the%20case%20began.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-arrests-six-months-after-custodial-death-despite-fir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ariana-Dalton%20split%20after%202%20years%20of%20marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689658152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101847258%2Cimgsize-48802.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2