20disappointed%20by%20the%20slowing%20pace%20of%20inspections%20and%20the%20exclusion%20of%20the%20port%20of%20Yuzhny%2FPivdennyi%20from%20the%20Black%20Sea%20Initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guterres%E2%80%99%20deputy%20spokesperson%2C%20Farhan%20Haq%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20side%20has%20been%20complaining%20that%20its%20demands%20are%20not%20being%20met%20and%20that%20Western%20sanctions%20are%20hindering%20the%20export%20of%20its%20own%20agricultural%20products.%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20argued%20to%20an%20African%20peace%20delegation%20earlier%20this%20week%20that%20the%20grain%20agreement%20did%20not%20solve%20the%20problems%20African%20countries%20had%20with%20high%20global%20food%20prices%2C%20because%20only%203%25%20of%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20grain%20exports%20go%20to%20the%20poorest%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20important%20is%20the%20Black%20Sea%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Black%20Sea%20is%20a%20strategic%20crossroads%20between%20southeastern%20Europe%20and%20Asia%2C%20a%20region%20where%20maritime%2C%20continental%2C%20geostrategic%20and%20economic%20interests%20come%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20only%20opportunity%20for%20Ukraine%20to%20export%20its%20grain%20to%20the%20world%20by%20sea.%20Access%20to%20the%20open%20sea%2C%20and%20thus%20an%20opportunity%20to%20access%20other%20export%20routes%2C%20is%20only%20possible%20via%20the%20Dardanelles%20and%20the%20Bosporus%20%E2%80%94%20both%20straits%20controlled%20by%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountries%20that%20border%20the%20Black%20Sea%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20the%20routes%20but%20the%20inland%20sea%20also%20plays%20a%20large%20economic%20role%20for%20China.%20As%20part%20of%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20New%20Silk%20Road%20project%2C%20the%20sea%20route%20across%20the%20Black%20Sea%20is%20supposed%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20better%20Chinese-European%20flow%20of%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E