ulse%2Fa-spent-force-a-kamtapur-militant-outfit-speaks-from-the-periphery-7968520%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeven%20greater%20demand%20of%C2%A0%20Kamatapur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20comprising%208%20districts%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%2015%20of%20Assam.%20In%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20area%20has%20witnessed%20large%20scale%20violent%20statehood%20movements%20by%20the%20Gorkhas%2C%20Rajbangshis%2C%20Kochs%20and%20Kamatapuris.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20region%20is%20sandwiched%20between%20Nepal%2C%20Bhutan%20on%20one%20side%20and%20Bangladesh%20on%20the%20south.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cchicken%E2%80%99s%20neck%E2%80%9D%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Siliguri%20Corridor%E2%80%99%20in%20north%20West%20Bengal%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20just%2021%20km%20wide%20and%2070%20km%20long%2C%20that%20connects%20the%20entire%20north-east%20India%20with%20the%20mainland%20remains%20a%20vulnerable%20region.%20More%20so%2C%20in%20recent%20years%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20expanding%20its%20chain%20of%20model%20villages%20close%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%2C%20130%20km%20away%2C%20which%20faces%20the%20strategically%20crucial%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecorridor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20two%20of%20BJPs%20Union%20ministers%20from%20Bengal%20have%20openly%20encouraged%20dismemberment%20of%20West%20Bengal%20much%20to%20the%20embarrassment%20of%20the%20other%20state%20leaders.%20After%20all%2C%20th%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ee%20Rajbangshis%20matter%20in%20only%20three%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Econstituencies%20and%20they%20fear%20losing%20the%20rest%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20BJP%20is%20the%20only%20all-India%20party%20that%20supports%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edemand%20for%20separation%20of%20the%20Darjeeling%20Hills%20from%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdarjeeling-bengal-hills-bjp-tmc-gjm-gorkhaland-gurung-tamang%5C%22%3EAnti-BJP%20Sentiments%20Stir%20Darjeeling%20Amidst%20Drastic%20Changes%20in%20Hill%20Party%20Equations%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20being%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98maharaja%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eholds%20considerable%20influence%20over%20the%20Koch-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbangshi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20community%20and%20has%20over%2018%20lakh%20followers%20accounting%20for%20nearly%202.4%25%20of%20voters%20in%20the%20state.%20Not%20all%20followers%20need%20be%20voters%20nor%20reside%20in%20the%20three%20districts%20of%20Alipurduar%2C%20Cooch%20Behar%20and%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20where%20they%20are%20concentrated.%20Besides%2C%20the%20other%20faction%20of%20the%20community%20led%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBangshibadan%20Barman%2C%20supports%20the%20TMC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20being%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethere%20are%2033%20lakh%20Rajbangshis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20projected%20current%20population%20of%20these%20three%20districts%20where%20they%20matter%20electorally%2C%20is%2076%20lakhs%20and%2030%25%20of%20them%20or%20about%2023%20lakhs%20are%20from%20the%20Rajbangshi%20community%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20So%20the%20remaining%2010%20lakhs%20are%20scattered%20insignificantly%20in%20other%20districts.%20Has%20the%20BJP%20gone%20wrong%20somewhere%20in%20their%20expected%20vote%20calculations%3F%20But%20that%20is%20not%20so%20important%20for%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnant%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20reported%20statement%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecreation%20of%20a%20new%20Union%20Territory%20(UT)%20in%20north%20Bengal%20was%20%E2%80%9Conly%20a%20matter%20of%20time%E2%80%9D%2C%20raises%20serious%20concern.%20Rajbangshis%20are%20spread%20over%20not%20only%20north%20Bengal%20but%20in%20parts%20of%20Assam%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Nepal%20and%20Bangladesh.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20fuelling%20any%20ethnic%20passion%20in%20this%20vulnerable%20region%20will%20be%20detrimental%20to%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20entire%20north-eastern%20part%20of%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20corner%20and%20dislodge%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20their%20central%20leaders%20to%20take%20the%20path%20of%20separatism.%20The%20people%20of%20Bengal%20went%20through%20a%20trauma%20when%20their%20second%20partition%20came%20in%201947.%20To%20add%20insult%20to%20that%20injury%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20commemorated%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhat%20the%20Governor%20%E2%80%9Cpeculiarly%20chose%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20State%20Foundation%20Day%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%9D%20on%20June%2020%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20never%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fciting-mamata-govts-neglect-bengal-bjp-chief-raises-pitch-for-trifurcation-demand%5C%22%3ECiting%20Mamata%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Neglect%E2%80%99%2C%20Bengal%20BJP%20Chief%20Raises%20Pitch%20for%20%E2%80%98Trifurcation%E2%80%99%20Demand%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-left-bjp%5C%22%3Eeffect%20on%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20not%20been%20good.%20In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20panchayat%20polls%2C%20the%20results%20of%20which%20have%20been%20temporarily%20withheld%20by%20the%20court%2C%20local%20media%20has%20unofficially%20estimated%20a%20sharp%20fall%20in%20their%20vote%20percentage%20from%2038%25%20in%202021%20to%2022%25%20in%202023.%20A%20whooping%20loss%20of%2016%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fcooch-behar-voters-division-west-bengal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20media%20shows%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emost%20people%20in%20Cooch%20Behar%20are%20against%20the%20separation%20of%20north%20Bengal.%20The%20locals%E2%80%99%20favouring%20BJP%20in%202021%20stemmed%20out%20of%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20failures%20and%20not%20out%20of%20support%20for%20separation%20from%20the%20state.%20The%20BJPs%20internal%20disconnect%20between%20the%20central%20and%20state%20leaders%20is%20clear.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20had%20dawned%20upon%20the%20British%20that%20to%20defeat%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20linguistic%20nationalism%20they%20needed%20to%20encourage%20religious%20nationalism.%20Similarly%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20it%20has%20dawned%20upon%20the%20BJP%20that%20as%20religious%20divisions%20have%20not%20worked%20among%20the%20Bengalis%20at%20large%2C%20they%20need%20to%20side%20with%20ethnic%20division%20to%20draw%20dividends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20satisfied%20with%20the%20breaking%20up%20of%20Bengal%20into%20east%20and%20west%2C%20which%20Syamaprasad%20Mukherjee%20of%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20supported%20in%201947%2C%20they%20are%20now%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fciting-mamata-govts-neglect-bengal-bjp-chief-raises-pitch-for-trifurcation-demand%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20media%20reports%20show%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20toeing%20the%20line%20of%20trifurcation%20of%20what%20is%20left%20of%20Bengal%20within%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20feared%20that%20forming%20UTs%20in%20this%20sensitive%20region%20with%20remote%20control%20from%20Delhi%20and%20reducing%20Bengal%20to%20south%20Bengal%20may%20have%20serious%20repercussions.%20One%20hopes%20that%20the%20authorities%20will%20not%20miss%20the%20woods%20for%20the%20trees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESumeru%20Roy%20Chaudhury%20is%20an%20architecture%20graduate%20from%20IIT%2C%20Kharagpur.%20He%20was%20the%20chief%20architect%20of%20the%20CPWD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689649040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16193248%2FF0msSp0aAAAGahL.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-divided-will-pull-in-several-different-ways%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20corner%20and%20dislodge%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20main%20reason%20as%20to%20why%20its%20central%20leaders%20have%20taken%20the%20path%20of%20separatism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-divided-will-pull-in-several-different-ways%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SAG-AFTRA%20Members%20Picket%20in%20High%20Heat%20to%20Show%20Solidarity%20and%20Prove%20That%20Strike%20is%20%E2%80%98Symptom%20of%20a%20Larger%20Problem%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689647863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FGF2_4770.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235672712%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20glimpse%20into%20the%20actor%E2%80%99s%20life%20in%20summer%202023%3A%20One%20day%20you%E2%80%99re%20nominated%20for%20your%20first%20Emmy%2C%20the%20next%20day%20your%20union%20goes%20on%20strike.%20Young%20Mazino%20is%20living%20just%20this%20reality%20after%20a%20whirlwind%20week%20that%20saw%20him%20land%20a%20supporting%20actor%20Emmy%