20autonomous%20vehicle%20in%20India.%20So%20when%20we%20took%20on%20the%20task%20of%20building%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%2C%20we%20also%20took%20up%20the%20task%20of%20building%20up%20an%20ecosystem%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gursimran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20also%20believe%20that%20the%20car%20is%20also%20a%20step%20towards%20safer%20roads%20as%20it%20eliminates%20the%20risks%20of%20human%20errors%20while%20driving.%20zPod%20can%20drive%20on%20any%20kind%20of%20environmental%20or%20geographical%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20duo%20was%20confident%20about%20their%20design%2C%20others%20were%20unsure%20if%20India%20was%20the%20right%20place%20to%20launch%20the%20vehicle.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20people%20who%20questioned%20us%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20move%20our%20innovation%20to%20a%20developed%20country%2C%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gagandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20raised%201.7%20million%20dollars%20in%20seed%20funding%20from%20various%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20this%20short%20video%20to%20find%20out%20how%20this%20driverless%20car%20works%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F2GjoR3mWM4E%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%