2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323767%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SWMRT%20team%20handled%20the%20waste%20collected%20during%20the%20wedding%20and%20composted%20it%20later.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLow-waste%20weddings%20are%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vasuki.%20%E2%80%9CBiodegradable%20waste%20is%20usually%20mixed%20with%20plastic%20waste%20and%20dumped%20in%20landfills.%20So%20our%20team%20was%20present%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20and%20we%20placed%20drums%20filled%20with%20cocopeat%20to%20collect%20the%20waste.%20We%20instructed%20the%20kitchen%2C%20catering%20and%20cleaning%20staff%20to%20segregate%20the%20waste%20and%20put%20the%20wet%20waste%20in%20the%20drums.%20The%20paper%20and%20flower%20waste%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20collection%20centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wet%20waste%20collected%20from%20the%20wedding%20was%20composted%20at%20the%20Swachagraha%20Kalika%20Kendra.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20by%20using%20steel%20cutlery%2C%2030%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F195354%2Fbengaluru-couple-eco-friendly-wedding-planning-tips-steel-cutlery-rent-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20disposables%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%2019-year-old%20butter%20paper%20for