article%20online%20on%20how%20there%20were%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20indigenous%20fruits%20that%20were%20being%20extinct.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20mentions%20of%20fruits%20that%20I%20have%20never%20even%20heard%20about%20and%20I%20was%20very%20shocked.%20For%20us%20fruits%20mostly%20mean%20the%20mainstream%20apples%2C%20mangoes%2C%20bananas%20and%20grapes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHearing%20about%20how%20so%20many%20tasty%20fruits%20are%20left%20ignored%20was%20sad%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20idea%20of%20putting%20them%20in%20chocolate%20came%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigvijay%20researched%20indigenously%20grown%20fruits%20such%20as%20kokam%2C%20ice%20apple%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20and%20tried%20them%20to%20discover%20which%20ones%20go%20well%20with%20chocolate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20culinary%20world%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20beyond%20exotic%20berries%2C%20cherries%20and%20oranges.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20a%20brand%20that%20puts%20anything%20else%20beyond%20the%20known%20few%20fruits.%20I%20wondered%20if%20there%20is%20a%20market%20for%20such%20chocolates%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20the%20business%20for%20only%20a%20few%20months%2C%20he%20was%20a%20little%20sceptical%20about%20this%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20the%20situation.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20lose%20such%20a%20great%20variety%20of%20fruits%20and%20also%20wanted%20to%20put%20them%20on%20a%20global%20map.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20tell%20people%20that%20%E2%80%98Hey!%20These%20fruits%20exist%20and%20I%20have%20put%20them%20in%20chocolate%20for%20you%20to%20try%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C