%20the%20primary%20colours%20of%20red%2C%20blue%20and%20green!%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photograph%20here%20depicts%20this%20form%20of%20photography%20and%20features%20sisters%20Amrita%20Sher%E2%80%93Gil%20and%20Indira%20Sher%E2%80%93Gil.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20their%20father%20Umrao%20Singh%20Sher%20Gil%2C%20a%20Sikh%20aristocrat%2C%20who%20shot%20it.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20that%20this%20picture%20made%20its%20way%20to%20the%20world%20as%20part%20of%20a%20project%20%E2%80%98Re-take%20of%20Amrita%E2%80%99%20by%20artist%20Vivan%20Sundaram%20(Indira%E2%80%99s%20son).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Ramaswamy%20Naidu%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F6c1d60646d19449d94607a3aa1db07c5_291340098_3127084117541921_859805760891268943_n-1688730812.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20'Three%20Nayar%20Girls%20of%20Travancore'%20is%20a%20famous%20painting%20by%20Ramaswamy%20Naidu%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F6c1d60646d19449d94607a3aa1db07c5_291340098_3127084117541921_859805760891268943_n-1688730812.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F6c1d60646d19449d94607a3aa1db07c5_291340098_3127084117541921_859805760891268943_n-1688730812-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F6c1d60646d19449d94607a3aa1db07c5_291340098_3127084117541921_859805760891268943_n-1688730812-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F6c1d60646d19449d94607a3aa1db07c5_291340098_3127084117541921_859805760891268943_n-1688730812-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%